  - added @{"groupfix.arccmd" link "groupfix.arccmd" 0}.
  - added grouplist for remote exporters.

 V1.0> (19.11.95)

  - changed the default for @{"groupfix.groupsvar" link "groupfix.groupsvar" 0} to @{"groupfix.subscribe" link "groupfix.subscribe" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.forwarddelay" link "groupfix.forwarddelay" 0}.
  - groupnames will no more be "case-changed".
  - added @{"groupfix.logfile" link "groupfix.logfile" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.loglevel" link "groupfix.loglevel" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.reportlevel" link "groupfix.reportlevel" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.groupfixname" link "groupfix.groupfixname" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.noaccess" link "groupfix.noaccess" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.help" link "groupfix.help" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.pwfailure" link "groupfix.pwfailure" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.groups.local" link "groupfix.groups.local" 0}.
  - added @{"groupfix.groups.<netname>" link "groupfix.groups.<netname>" 0}.
  - added ums.log-support.

